    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of BMW\u2019s M-Division engineering. At its heart is the S54 3.2L high-revving straight-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that has been professionally overhauled for peak volumetric efficiency. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement, ensuring the integrity of the rear suspension mounting points. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory limited-slip differential. The vehicle exhibits zero fluid seepage, crisp throttle response, and a suspension profile that retains its original damping characteristics. A true collector-grade specimen with no mechanical or aesthetic deficiencies.",
