      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, appearing exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster with zero swirl marks, scratches, or stone chips, thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating and consistent climate-controlled garage storage. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather upholstery shows no signs of wear or bolster compression, the carpets are pristine, and it still carries that distinct new-car scent. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach. It has been exclusively serviced at authorized dealerships on a time-based schedule rather than just mileage, with a comprehensive binder of every service record included to document its pampered life. Every button, switch, and electronic feature functions flawlessly. With incredibly low mileage and a history of meticulous adult ownership, this is a rare opportunity for a collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that is indistinguishable from new. Sale includes both original keys, all factory manuals, and a custom-fitted breathable car cover.",
